```html
<script type="module">
    import { Game } from './game.js';
    window.game = new Game();
    window.game.initialize();
</script>
```

to:

```html
<script type="module">
    import Game from './game.js';
    window.game = new Game();
    window.game.initialize();
</script>
```

Please replace the corresponding line in your index.html file with this one. Now, the Game class should be imported properly as the default export from the game.js file.

